Defendant Abdulla Eminovski in court with attorney Michael J Steinle.  Defendant Abdulla Eminovski in custody.  Brad Alan Vorpahl appeared for the State of Wisconsin.   Deputy court clerk: LMS.

Defendant has picked up a new felony case.  The defendant is not in compliance with the terms of the Deferred Prosecution Agreement.  Based upon the defendant's non-compliance and State's motion, the court revoked the Deferred Prosecution Agreement; proceedings reinstated.  Court orders entry of Judgment of Conviction.

Sentencing proceeded.  Statements made as to sentencing.
Court sentenced defendant to serve 30 DAYS in the House of Correction CONSECUTIVE to any sentence with credit for 17 days served; Straight time. Court recommends against electronic monitoring. 

Court orders defendant to pay all cost, fees and surcharges, including DNA surcharge by 10/07/2015 or a civil judgment to be entered with tax intercept.  Bail on deposit to be applied if applicable.
